## **_WOMEN'S INTERCONTINENTAL CHAMPIONSHIP: LYRA VALKYRIA DEF. IVY NILE_**

Lyra and Ivy have a fun and physical sprint that ends with Lyra on top.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cce514bf-c685-4448-959f-157b5342ca8d/Messenger_creation_1544707759543746.jpeg?format=original)

CM Punk and Seth Rollins find each backstage and get into another brawl.

Adam Pearce tells Seth Rollins that he's putting him in a bad position. Rollins says Pearce knows what he has to do.

Rollins and CM Punk have to finish this!!

CM PUNK VS SETH ROLLINS IN A STEEL CAGE!! NEXT WEEK IN MADISON SQUARE GARDEN!!

